  "detailed_description": "<h1>ADD TO YOUR WISHLIST</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.poster.avif?t=1700670002\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.webm?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/ef0dcd45bf41e034243005a2e364a55b.mp4?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>The islands are sinking... Chickenfolk can't swim and fox bandits won't miss an opportunity to gobble up a bird or two even on the verge of apocalypse... What a disaster!<br>Fortunately Big Chick is here to save the day! Use poultry magic to summon new patches of land from the ocean depths and micromanagement skills to lead your people to the safety of the sacred Big Barn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/24fce2863ac907dda4ee3dcfda238d9f.poster.avif?t=1700670002\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/24fce2863ac907dda4ee3dcfda238d9f.webm?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/24fce2863ac907dda4ee3dcfda238d9f.mp4?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure on the sinking islands features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>cute and adorable chickens</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>nasty (but cute anyway) foxes and other predators</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>frantic gameplay</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>doomsday atmosphere</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/bc74ec0a0f8706ac8f1cfc006113bfe2.poster.avif?t=1700670002\" width=480 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/bc74ec0a0f8706ac8f1cfc006113bfe2.webm?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/bc74ec0a0f8706ac8f1cfc006113bfe2.mp4?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "The islands are sinking... Chickenfolk can't swim and fox bandits won't miss an opportunity to gobble up a bird or two even on the verge of apocalypse... What a disaster!<br>Fortunately Big Chick is here to save the day! Use poultry magic to summon new patches of land from the ocean depths and micromanagement skills to lead your people to the safety of the sacred Big Barn.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/24fce2863ac907dda4ee3dcfda238d9f.poster.avif?t=1700670002\" width=600 height=344 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/24fce2863ac907dda4ee3dcfda238d9f.webm?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/24fce2863ac907dda4ee3dcfda238d9f.mp4?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Adventure on the sinking islands features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>cute and adorable chickens</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>nasty (but cute anyway) foxes and other predators</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>frantic gameplay</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>doomsday atmosphere</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/bc74ec0a0f8706ac8f1cfc006113bfe2.poster.avif?t=1700670002\" width=480 height=430 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/bc74ec0a0f8706ac8f1cfc006113bfe2.webm?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1406000/extras/bc74ec0a0f8706ac8f1cfc006113bfe2.mp4?t=1700670002\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
